{"tid":1846671,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果一個武漢肺炎支那種上咗巴士咳，會唔會巴士上大部份人都瀨野？","createTime":"2020-01-27T16:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T17:02:42.000Z","uid":20272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"68acfcd9d5e4e2105d5041b762c59c62b393cf40","tid":1846671,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:50:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返工放工搭巴士，好撚驚"},{"pid":"1843302500afa8bd05942c3f48c3eff051d0bcfc","tid":1846671,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:53:28.000Z","msg":"巴士入面既空氣咁唔流通<br />\n假設個支那種係樓梯/落車位附近咳，全部人都要經過。。。"},{"pid":"2d62e13b8af01b687430b74c31f7da3681398907","tid":1846671,"uid":165232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:56:02.000Z","msg":"你还有党呀"},{"pid":"846ade94cf405dc51c9b44c577d6fad204b42206","tid":1846671,"uid":86674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:56:16.000Z","msg":"唔會，但係好容易喪屍式傳染<br />\n病毒重過空氣，會係下降果陣<br />\n黏係啲座位、手把、扶手、欄杆到<br />\n就咁空氣傳唔到幾多個<br />\n<br />\n但係當佢傳比第二個人，之後果個人再咳<br />\n就會喪屍式咁傳<br />\n所以手套好緊要，你見啲醫護一定戴手套<br />\n反而有時會唔記得口罩，但係一定有手套"},{"pid":"5441ab20a32a46527cad5cb1cb95188a9096750b","tid":1846671,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:58:42.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n1.增派警員至各關口增援，減輕海關負擔<br />\n2.增派警員到醫院駐守，以防有病人逃走<br />\n3.增派警員在各區巡邏，以防止香港人口突然大增，導致治安問題<br />\n4.每30個內地求診者，配2名警員帶路至醫院或警署<br />\n5.警員不準歧視戴口罩者為暴徒。<br />\n<br />\n咁撚鐘意帶人黎香港就要負責番啲內地人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3e3uQHc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3e3uQHc.jpg&h=10ef4d8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wwTFXnd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwwTFXnd.jpg&h=76d85795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hDaw32d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhDaw32d.jpg&h=2442c6c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/75iCe8U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F75iCe8U.jpg&h=c4437dbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wCFUhne.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwCFUhne.jpg&h=c2768323&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"708cbf91ed541c3b12bb50fb3f32202341f1ceed","tid":1846671,"uid":239812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:02:42.000Z","msg":"兩次食飯 兩次都有仆街大聲咳唔帶口罩唔掩嘴"}]}